"The patches stored in the newer <literal>3.0 (quilt)</literal> source format "
"must be <emphasis>fuzz</emphasis> free.  You should ensure it as "
"<literal>dquilt pop -a; while dquilt push; do dquilt refresh; done</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Els pegats conservats amb el nou format de fonts <literal>3.0 (quilt)</"
"literal> han d'estar <emphasis>exempts</emphasis> de coses innecessàries.  "
"Pots comprovar-ho executant <literal>quilt pop -a; while quilt push; do "
"quilt refresh; done</literal>."

