"Descriu abreujadament els canvis realitzats <emphasis>en les fonts originals "
"per l'autor</emphasis> que solucionen errors informats i tanca els informes "
"d'aquests errors"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Describe concisely the changes <emphasis>to the new upstream release</"
#| "emphasis> by the maintainer that fix reported bugs and close those bugs."
msgid ""
"Describe concisely the changes <emphasis>to the new upstream release</"
"emphasis> by the maintainer that fix reported bugs and close those bugs by "
"adding <literal>Closes: #<replaceable>bug_number</replaceable></literal>."
msgstr ""
"Descriu abreujadament els canvis realitzats <emphasis>a les fonts originals</"
"emphasis> pel desenvolupador (tu mateix en aquest cas) per solucionar els "
"errors informats i tanca els informes."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "<literal>while quilt push; do quilt refresh; done</literal> to apply all "
