"Executa <literal>while quilt push; do quilt refresh; done</literal> per "
"aplicar els pegats eliminat <emphasis>les coses innecessàries</emphasis>."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><para>
msgid ""
"If the patch/merge did not apply cleanly, inspect the situation (clues are "
